parser

Class State

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.State
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<State>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BRTDP.SearchState, BRTDP.SearchState

    public class State
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<State>
    Class to store a model state, i.e. a mapping from variables to values. Stores as an array of Objects, where indexing is defined by a model.
